258
00:11:52,160 --> 00:11:53,720
It sounded so official.

259
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,600
And I was doing it.

260
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,240
And I had this massive idea.

261
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,600
I would create this global network of thousands

262
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,320
of women from all over the world

263
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,760
and help to inspire them and connect them

264
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:06,360
and just help to empower them to build successful businesses.

265
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:09,720
But I had no idea how I was going to do this.

266
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:12,440
So then I was like, right, I need to program my mind

267
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,160
to make this happen.

268
00:12:14,160 --> 00:12:16,240
So I started by becoming consciously aware

269
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:18,600
of all the things I was thinking of every day.

270
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,760
And whenever I'd catch myself thinking something like,

271
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:23,600
carry, who is going to come to this website?

272
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,280
Who are you to give advice to anyone?

273
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,240
This is rubbish.

274
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,680
This is a ridiculous idea.

275
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:29,400
You're never going to be able to do it.

276
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:31,760
Every time I call myself saying something like that,

277
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:33,280
I would stop myself.

278
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:35,440
And I realized that I had the power

279
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:37,360
to take control over my thoughts

280
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:39,640
rather than letting them control me.

281
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:43,960
I knew that I could stop myself from thinking these things.

282
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,800
And I did.

283
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:47,960
I replaced the negative, rubbish, annoying thoughts

284
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,400
and told them to shut up.

285
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:51,920
And I replaced them with positive thoughts

286
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:53,320
that were empowering me.

287
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,240
Thoughts that were actually helping me

288
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:57,160
to move towards my goal.

289
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:59,680
I also started to listen to guided visualizations

290
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:02,280
to program my subconscious mind for success.

291
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:06,000
And I got really into doing visualizations, vividly

292
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:09,640
picturing what I wanted to achieve, seeing it happen,

293
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:11,880
and then feeling it happen like it was happening right

294
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:15,560
then and there, just like all the top athletes do.

295
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:18,920
I got so clear on what I wanted to make happen.

296
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:22,880
And since then, my life has totally changed.

297
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:25,120
I felt one of the largest online networking groups

298
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:28,680
of female entrepreneurs with over 100,000 women involved.

299
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:30,640
And then I came up with this crazy idea

300
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:32,640
to launch a digital magazine, which then

301
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:34,480
became the fastest-growing digital magazine

302
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,880
for female entrepreneurs.

303
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:37,920
And when I created it, I made this wish list

304
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:40,480
in my mind of all the people I wanted on the front cover,

305
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:43,760
these best-selling authors, these incredibly successful

306
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:44,840
entrepreneurs.

307
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,560
I had no idea how would make it happen,

308
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:48,480
but I was so convinced it would.

309
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:51,920
I then put their faces on mockups of the front cover,

310
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:54,480
printed them off and stuck them on my goal board,

311
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:57,440
and just visualized them being on the front cover,

312
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,840
visualized what it would feel like the moment I would send out

313
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:01,200
an email to my network.

314
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,960
And I could say to them, hey, everyone,

315
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:05,680
this person's on the front cover this month, how exciting.

316
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:08,760
I got so unbelievably clear about what I want to do

317
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:10,080
and when people would come up to me and say,

318
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:12,240
carry, how are you going to make this happen?

319
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:15,040
I was like, don't know, but I'm going to make it happen.

320
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:16,240
And it did happen.

321
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:19,120
So then I thought to myself, well, what other crazy goals

322
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,040
could I make happen?

323
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:21,840
What else is possible?

324
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,520
So I set more crazy goals myself.

325
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:26,240
I was like, hell, I want to go to Buckingham Palace.

326
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,840
I want to go to the House of Lords.

327
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:29,600
I want to speak at the House of Commons.

328
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:32,280
And I set more crazy goals for myself.

329
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:35,200
And last year, every single one of them happened.

330
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:40,720
And I realized that if I could get my mind to be certain

331
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,960
that I could make something happen,

332
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:46,160
that somehow I would figure out a way.

333
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:50,760
And I always have, because success is no accident.

334
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:54,480
Living an incredible life is no accident.

335
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:56,680
You have to do it on purpose.

336
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:59,160
And it starts by knowing exactly what it is

337
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,320
that you want to achieve.

